{"tid":1086354,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣布 用魚柳包果隻他他醬點魚生刺身完全屌打豉油芥辣","createTime":"2019-03-31T17:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T14:55:26.000Z","uid":171273,"like":5,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0f9d6f654817eedf1d5b81ea835e3c99cb6cae81","tid":1086354,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T17:22:51.000Z","msg":"大家可能食過花之戀/加州卷/青龍捲呢類新式壽司<br />\n<br />\n都發現入面有用到蛋黃醬黎增加香味<br />\n<br />\n我平時食呢d壽司都一定唔點豉油 因為已經夠味<br />\n<br />\n點豉油會破壞個感覺<br />\n<br />\n但係食魚生偏偏大多數地方都無得點mayonnaise<br />\n<br />\n不過我諗大家都覺得蛋黃醬呢家野太肥 好易膩<br />\n<br />\n所以我諗到用有蛋黃醬做底既他他醬黎代替豉油<br />\n<br />\n不但有mayonnaise既香味 再加上佢加入左酸瓜/parsley/洋蔥同capers等等既材料<br />\n<br />\n不但更有層次地香 略帶酸味亦都可以解膩 仲要越食越開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而他他醬同魚有幾夾 只要有食過魚柳包我諗都唔需要多解釋<br />\n<br />\n試完咁食幾次之後完全覺得日本人用豉油點魚生扮哂正宗呢種心態好撚不可一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：係公司樓下citysuper買刺身級既魚生 <br />\n他他醬都係citysuper買 買左a&amp;p 50蚊果隻"},{"pid":"4bd2084abea66373104e51f49c688de768834458","tid":1086354,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T17:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a067b0e3a1fb25a2662844ed0237512e63846f","tid":1086354,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T17:23:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f66a9ea1459a56ba899aba6ba53d4e50eed48b","tid":1086354,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T17:24:01.000Z","msg":"樓主識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e003f0c6e52c87d1671e9a35378028dce15cc7ee","tid":1086354,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T17:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578e3427eca4cd09df99aabd7c71